as I remembered you.

Tuck

messages.subject: The Vilter Family Photo
messages.msgSnippet: I ve uploaded a photo of the Vilter family. I spent some time looking for one that was taken in this century and couldn t find one we all liked so we took this
messages.messageBody:
I've uploaded a photo of the Vilter family. I spent some time looking for
one that was taken in this century and couldn't find one we all liked so we
took this one today. Sandra, thanks for motivating us. Now I have something
to send my brothers and friends.

Thanks all of you who have posted photos. It is very nice to have a picture
to connect the names to.

-Dan Vilter
